{"tid":2090781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人會申請澳洲專俾香港人申請嘅新790visa","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T11:40:17.000Z","uid":13251,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"230fb37269f8b493455544bc95ea126dfd13abbe","tid":2090781,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589062167776847/posts/3628006110549089/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589062167776847%2Fposts%2F3628006110549089%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8EYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=9a9db27d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589062167776847/posts/3628006110549089/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8541290944777eaa179a025118e01d73552ce6c","tid":2090781,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"Who is a refugee<br />\nTo be a refugee in Australia, an asylum seeker must be assessed as meeting certain legal criteria. The meaning of a 'refugee' in the Migration Act 1958 (the Act) is a person in Australia who is:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">outside their country of nationality or former habitual residence</span> (their home country) and<br />\nowing to a 'well-founded fear of persecution', is unable or unwilling to return to their home country or to seek the protection of that country<br />\nThe definition is forward-looking. Even if a person has suffered persecution in the past, they are not a refugee by the meaning in the Act unless they have a well-founded fear of persecution and there is a real chance they will be persecuted in their home country now, if they were to return. However, past events could establish a real chance of persecution if the person were to return.<br />\n<br />\nA person might become a refugee after arriving in Australia. This could occur if there is a change of circumstances in their home country or a change in personal circumstances after they left that gives them a well-founded fear of persecution if they were to return.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4f5f22fd96ab5e579edb08135027a7fab549ca","tid":2090781,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:37:51.000Z","msg":"Cost<br />\nAUD40<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb703763f844b86882c9f08d540f6758e64192e","tid":2090781,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"access government services such as Centrelink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bf9e68fb105b3e770dc6af627bc5badec207c8","tid":2090781,"uid":194209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"但要住regional<br />\n同埋要睇下點駁番pr pathway"},{"pid":"427460448b8ac410644353ea27ac1eefde4449de","tid":2090781,"uid":13251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9bf9e68fb105b3e770dc6af627bc5badec207c8","tid":2090781,"uid":194209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"但要住regional<br />\n同埋要睇下點駁番pr pathway"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"咁要努力讀書 賺錢投資 結婚等等<br />\n你都唔想去到做蝗蟲啦<br />\n同埋5年唔得可以再續5年"},{"pid":"6b4f3e78ce0625b7f12c037ccba83d9771fceda0","tid":2090781,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9bf9e68fb105b3e770dc6af627bc5badec207c8","tid":2090781,"uid":194209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:43:28.000Z","msg":"但要住regional<br />\n同埋要睇下點駁番pr pathway"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"邊到寫regional?"},{"pid":"03a671d7f7726668d94179ac4e8e7dcd3ffd34f8","tid":2090781,"uid":194209,"like":0,"dislike":